articles.title: Europe's Ariane 5 rocket lifts off for final time - DW (English)
articles.description: The European Space Agency's Ariane 5 "workhorse" rocket has marked its 117th and final mission on Thursday after 27 years of service.
articles.content:
The European Space Agency said its Ariane 5 rocket successfully took off from French Guinea for the final time on Wednesday night.
